<abstract><t>This document describes an automated enterprise vulnerability assessment scenario aligned with the SACM Use Cases.  The scenario assumes the existence of an endpoint management capability and begins with an enterprise ingesting vulnerability description information. Endpoints are assessed against the vulnerability description information based on a combination of examining known endpoint characterization information and collected endpoint information.</t></abstract>

